article_title: 5 Health Insurance Stocks Struggling to Hold Gains
article_text:
Jim Cramer's 'Mad Money' Recap: These Stocks Still Sweet Despite Sour Market

There are lots of stocks still working in this market, and Cramer tells you which ones.

article_metadata.description: Obamacare enrollments may be declining but industry mergers are increasing, affecting Aetna (AET), Anthem (ANTM), Cigna (CI), Centene (CNC) and UnitedHeath (UNH).
article_metadata.author: Richard Suttmeier
